Заполнение пропущенных значений¶

In [6]:
#    is_apartment  False.
data['is_apartment'] = data['is_apartment'].fillna(False)

#    balcony 0.
data['balcony'] = data['balcony'].fillna(0)

#    ceiling_height     
for locality_name in data['locality_name'].unique():
  median = data.loc[data['locality_name'] == locality_name, 'ceiling_height'].median()
  data.loc[(data['ceiling_height'].isna()) & (data['locality_name'] == locality_name), 'ceiling_height'] = median
#    ceiling_height  ,      
data.loc[data['ceiling_height'].isna(), 'ceiling_height'] = data['ceiling_height'].median()

#     ,           ,       .
ratio_total_living = data['total_area'][data['living_area'].isnull() == True].mean() / data['living_area'][data['living_area'].isnull() == False].mean()
#            ratio_total_living
data['living_area'] = data['living_area'].fillna(data['total_area'] / ratio_total_living)

#     ,           ,       .
ratio_total_kitchen = data['total_area'][data['kitchen_area'].isnull() == True].mean() / data['kitchen_area'][data['kitchen_area'].isnull() == False].mean()
#            ratio_total_kitchen
data['kitchen_area'] = data['kitchen_area'].fillna(data['total_area'] / ratio_total_kitchen)

#    cityCenters_nearest     
for locality_name in data['locality_name'].unique():
  median = data.loc[data['locality_name'] == locality_name, 'cityCenters_nearest'].median()
  data.loc[(data['cityCenters_nearest'].isna()) & (data['locality_name'] == locality_name), 'cityCenters_nearest'] = median
    
#    airports_nearest     
for locality_name in data['locality_name'].unique():
  median = data.loc[data['locality_name'] == locality_name, 'airports_nearest'].median()
  data.loc[(data['airports_nearest'].isna()) & (data['locality_name'] == locality_name), 'airports_nearest'] = median
    
#    parks_nearest     
for locality_name in data['locality_name'].unique():
  median = data.loc[data['locality_name'] == locality_name, 'parks_nearest'].median()
  data.loc[(data['parks_nearest'].isna()) & (data['locality_name'] == locality_name), 'parks_nearest'] = median
    
    
#    ponds_nearest     
for locality_name in data['locality_name'].unique():
  median = data.loc[data['locality_name'] == locality_name, 'ponds_nearest'].median()
  data.loc[(data['ponds_nearest'].isna()) & (data['locality_name'] == locality_name), 'ponds_nearest'] = median

#   ,  
def category_price_def(row):
    price = row['last_price']
    if price < 1000000:
        return ' 1 '
    elif 1000000 <= price < 2000000:
        return ' 1  2 '
    elif 2000000 <= price < 3000000:
        return ' 2  3 '
    elif 3000000 <= price < 4000000:
        return ' 3  4 '
    elif 4000000 <= price < 5000000:
        return ' 4  5 '
    elif 5000000 <= price < 6000000:
        return ' 5  6 '  
    elif 6000000 <= price < 7000000:
        return ' 6  7 '     
    else:
        return ' 7 '      

data['category_price'] = data.apply(category_price_def, axis = 1)
data.groupby('category_price', as_index=False)[['last_price']].count().sort_values('category_price', ascending=True)
